name: #1 POSTCARD FROM BUENOS AIRES
description:
This is my first postcard mint.
As a beginning, it has to be from my home: Buenos Aires.

This is one of the 30k postcards that I create to finance my travels around the world. I sold them on the street to pay for my days traveling.

EL VIAJE DE MIS FOTOS are the creations that served me not only to finance myself but they were the reason I had to connect with people, just as they are here today.
